title: Virtual Member
body: With a Virtual Office membership, we offer a desirable downtown mailing address as well as access to internal and external events. Hassle-free mail service is a great way to jumpstart your business, so get started today at Awesome Inc.

title: Open Desk Member
body: An Open Desk Membership allows you at have 24-hour access to a quiet, yet collaborative workspace in downtown Lexington. With a membership, you will receive unlimited printing, conference room time in one of our two conference rooms and access to internal and external events.
